{{- /* Clawbot-only seed of ~/.aws/credentials with PLACEHOLDER profiles: the
       caged agent signs AWS requests with fake AKIDs that the gateway's
       aws_sso_credential maps to roles and re-signs with real SSO-minted creds
       (see private/clawtilla/gateway.hcl). Real creds never reach the agent.

       The profiles are account-specific (names + placeholder AKIDs mirror the
       accounts), so the content lives in the private overlay, never the public
       repo — same idiom as the other private-overlay symlinks (e.g.
       app-log-investigation). stat-guarded, so the public repo stands alone and a
       human box (whose overlay carries no such file) keeps its real
       ~/.aws/credentials untouched; on a clawbot the overlay supplies the file and
       this symlink resolves. */ -}}
{{- $src := joinPath .chezmoi.sourceDir ".." "private" "home" "aws" "credentials" -}}
{{- if stat $src }}{{ $src }}{{ end -}}
